flowchart TB
    User[User or automation]
    CLI[tau_coding CLI]
    TUI[Textual TUI]
    CodingSession[tau_coding CodingSession]
    Harness[tau_agent AgentHarness]
    AgentLoop[tau_agent run_agent_loop]
    Provider[tau_ai ModelProvider]
    Tools[tau_coding read/write/edit/bash tools]
    Storage[append-only JSONL sessions]
    Resources[skills prompts AGENTS.md resources]

    User --> CLI
    CLI --> TUI
    CLI --> CodingSession
    TUI --> CodingSession
    CodingSession --> Harness
    Harness --> AgentLoop
    AgentLoop --> Provider
    AgentLoop --> Tools
    CodingSession --> Storage
    CodingSession --> Resources

    Provider -- provider events --> AgentLoop
    AgentLoop -- agent events --> Harness
    Harness -- agent events --> CodingSession
    CodingSession -- projected state --> TUI
